strings: <se_high>*: For a long time, there were no strangers in this arid desert.
<se_high>*: It was very crowded here. Nobody is coming now.
<se_high>*: It's the cursed spike of Troden Castle in the north. very annoyed
<se_low>*: I've heard there's a magic key from Castle Truden. I ran and I could not believe my eyes.
<se_low>*: I don't want to interfere, but if I were you, I wouldn't do it. You might even experience the curse!
<se_low>*: I'm sorry, I don't want to now because I'm scared...
<se_low>*: It doesn't matter because we don't forget it and move on.
